got its name.

190
00:07:13.767 --> 00:07:15.233
Sand dollars
are really lucky.

191
00:07:15.367 --> 00:07:17.800
- Uncle Brody says
Sand Dollar Cove

192
00:07:17.934 --> 00:07:19.767
