a resort hotel on the beach.

216
00:08:08.166 --> 00:08:09.800
- That's great.
That's great news.

217
00:08:09.934 --> 00:08:11.433
You know.

218
00:08:11.567 --> 00:08:14.000
I want to show you
that Sand Dollar Cove

219
00:08:14.133 --> 00:08:15.834
