the pier?

232
00:08:41.100 --> 00:08:43.000
Sorry I'm late. Holden.
Forgive me.

233
00:08:43.133 --> 00:08:45.800
- Oh. that's all right.
I understand. Brody.

234
00:08:45.934 --> 00:08:49.133
