to registering the deeds yet.

245
00:09:14.734 --> 00:09:16.500
- I thought you owned
that bait and tackle shop.

246
00:09:16.633 --> 00:09:17.667
- I do.

247
00:09:17.800 --> 00:09:19.767
The bait and tackle shop.
the pier.

248
00:09:19.900 --> 00:09:22.867
