1829
01:17:56.166 --> 01:17:57.967
- She left?

1830
01:17:58.100 --> 01:18:00.467
After the way you two
were dancing last night?

1831
01:18:00.600 --> 01:18:01.900
- Yeah.

1832
01:18:03.333 --> 01:18:05.767
I guess looks can be deceiving.
