1833
01:18:05.900 --> 01:18:07.767
- Oh. Brody.

1834
01:18:07.900 --> 01:18:09.867
- I know.

1835
01:18:11.500 --> 01:18:14.333
I know I only knew her
a few weeks. but...

1836
01:18:15.934 --> 01:18:18.400
it just felt...

1837
01:18:19.800 --> 01:18:21.266
- Well. if you really
have feelings for Elli.

1838
01:18:21.400 --> 01:18:22.867
you need to try
